{"entry":{"name":"ofxXmlSettings","filename":"ofxXmlSettings","absolute":"/Users/Gilbert/Code/openFrameworks/ofSite/documentation/addons/ofxXmlSettings","path":"/documentation/addons/ofxXmlSettings/","dir":"../ofSite/documentation/addons","route":"/documentation/addons/ofxXmlSettings/","ext":"","type":"folder","id":176,"children":[177,178,179],"parent":26,"breadcrumbs":[26,1],"siblings":[],"translations":{}},"intro":{"name":"introduction","filename":"introduction.markdown","absolute":"/Users/Gilbert/Code/openFrameworks/ofSite/documentation/addons/ofxXmlSettings/introduction.markdown","path":"/documentation/addons/ofxXmlSettings/introduction","route":"/documentation/addons/ofxXmlSettings/introduction.markdown","dir":"../ofSite/documentation/addons/ofxXmlSettings","ext":"markdown","type":"page","id":177,"parent":176,"breadcrumbs":[176,26,1],"translations":{"ko":{"name":"introduction-ko","filename":"introduction.ko.markdown","absolute":"/Users/Gilbert/Code/openFrameworks/ofSite/documentation/application/introduction.ko.markdown","path":"/documentation/application/introduction-ko","route":"/documentation/application/introduction.ko.markdown","dir":"../ofSite/documentation/application","ext":"markdown","type":"page","id":181,"parent":180,"breadcrumbs":[180,1],"siblings":[{"name":"introduction-ko","filename":"introduction.ko.markdown","absolute":"/Users/Gilbert/Code/openFrameworks/ofSite/documentation/glm/introduction.ko.markdown","path":"/documentation/glm/introduction-ko","route":"/documentation/glm/introduction.ko.markdown","dir":"../ofSite/documentation/glm","ext":"markdown","type":"page","id":356,"parent":268,"breadcrumbs":[268,1],"siblings":[],"translations":{}},{"name":"introduction-ko","filename":"introduction.ko.markdown","absolute":"/Users/Gilbert/Code/openFrameworks/ofSite/documentation/graphics/introduction.ko.markdown","path":"/documentation/graphics/introduction-ko","route":"/documentation/graphics/introduction.ko.markdown","dir":"../ofSite/documentation/graphics","ext":"markdown","type":"page","id":364,"parent":358,"breadcrumbs":[358,1],"siblings":[],"translations":{}}],"translations":{}}},"siblings":[]},"document":"<h2>Simple XML loader and saver</h2>\n<p>ofxXmlSettings allows you to save data to an xml file and to read data from it.\nIt can be useful, for example, if your OF application is collecting data and you want to\nexport them at the end of the process, or if you want to initialize your\napplication reading values from an xml configuration.</p>\n<p>In order to use it, include it in your <code>ofApp<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>h</code></p>\n<pre><code><span class=\"token macro property\">#<span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> &amp;quot;ofxXmlSettings.h&amp;quot;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ofApp</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> ofBaseApp<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\">// ...</span>\n    ofxXmlSettings XML<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\">// ...</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>To load a file, in your <code>ofApp<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>cpp</code> class</p>\n<pre><code>XML<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">loadFile</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>quot<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>mySettings<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>xml<span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>quot<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>In the example folder <code>example<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>addons<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>xmlSettingsExample</code> you can see how to\nread field from the xml, add new ones, or change the value of existing ones</p>\n","type":"folder"}